Package: flexlsx
Type: Package
Title: Exporting 'flextable' to Excel
Version: 0.1.4
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Tobias",
                   family = "Heidler",
                   role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
                   email = "tobias.heidler@googlemail.com",
                   comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9193-0980")))
Description: Exports 'flextable' tables to Excel-Sheets using 'openxlsx2'.
    Objects that can be converted to 'flextable' objects (e.g. 'gtsummary') 
    can be exported as well.
